l-brac\">)</span></span> to <a href=\"/wiki/get_lost\" title=\"get lost\">get lost</a>\n<dl><dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Ils se sont <b>perdus</b> dans la forêt dense.</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">They got lost in the dense forest.</span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></li>\n<li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\"><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#transitive\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">transitive</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> to <a href=\"/wiki/waste\" title=\"waste\">waste</a>, to make bad use of something\n<dl><dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Je crois que la journée est trop belle pour qu'on la perde.</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">I think the day is too nice to waste.</span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl>\n<ul><li><div class=\"citation-whole\"><span class=\"cited-source\"><span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\"><b>1943</b></span>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antoine_Saint-Exup%C3%A9ry\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Antoine Saint-Exupéry\">Antoine Saint-Exupéry</a>, chapter XXI, in <cite>Le petit prince</cite> [<cite><span class=\"e-translation\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Little_Prince\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:The Little Prince\">The Little Prince</a></span></cite>], New York: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reynal_%26_Hitchcock\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Reynal &amp; Hitchcock\">Reynal &amp; Hitchcock</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.org/details/le-petit-prince-antoine-st-ex-livre/page/n82/mode/1up\">page <span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\">83</span></a>:</span><dl><dd><div class=\"h-quotation\"><span class=\"Latn e-quotation cited-passage\" lang=\"fr\">C'est le temps que tu as <b>perdu</b> pour ta rose qui fait ta rose si importante.</span><dl><dd><span class=\"e-tra